title: American Horror Story Season 10 Update
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: My husband and I have been together since 2010, married since 2019, and we've been living together for about 6 years now. He has always given me crap because I refuse to buy TP in small packs, it's not cost effective and you're going to use it anyway so why not buy the biggest pack you can? He finally understands my point now, right before everyone started going crazy and panic buying I went and picked up a giant pack, like I always do, and we've literally kept our house and both our parents stocked with our pack. California is crazy with all the quarantine, over buying, and price gouging.
i would love to do a stream with you i have so many theories

I’m still angry, my husband was exposed in February when trump was making a joke of this. 
I was so sick for over 4 weeks and couldn’t get tested, (dr didn’t want me to go out anyway because of my heart & immunodeficiency etc) chronic fatigue was multiplied, extreme flu symptoms, high fevers, massive headaches, difficulty breathing, lung pain I’d never experienced before... my lungs still aren’t working right and the weakness lingers. It’s listed as unknown respiratory virus.
GRRL I told my mom to get toilet paper so much that I have a room full seriously :P
